reviews.review_text: suprise, suprise!!! If you like suprises then this is your show! On the heels of the disappointing 15th anniversery show the boys unleash the goods from the get-go. UJB>playing>UJB begins today's proceedings. Great taste but Lesh filling! Phil is a beast as is Jerry. Very nice opening. The rest of the 1st set is "normal" but nicely played. The 2nd set has its moments (eyes), but orgasim was achieved early on leaving only a smoke and a nap.
